    Netsu Design Blow Dry Cream
    shuuemuraartofhair-usa.comManufacturer

    Description

    Achieve a more polished finish with the Shu Uemura blow-dry cream. From The Art Of Styling collection, the line takes inspiration from the Japanese art of minimalism, stripping the formula down to only the necessary components to deliver real results. Taken from the Japanese word for heat, the Netsu cream strives to safeguard the strands. Protecting the hair up to 230C, the formula helps to reduce the breakage and damage caused by heat styling. MORE
    Ingredient: Beeswax, Camellia Oil, Hydroxyethylcellulose, Isopropyl Myristate
    Purpose: Anti-frizz, Damage, Frizz Control, Heat Protecting, Holding, Treatment
    Size: 147.9 ml
    Type: Cream, Mask

    Shu Uemura Netsu Design Blow Dry Cream

    4.6(253)
    Achieve a more polished finish with the Shu Uemura blow-dry cream. From The Art Of Styling collection, the line takes inspiration from the Japanese art of minimalism, stripping the formula down to only the necessary components to deliver real results. Taken from the Japanese word for heat, the Netsu cream strives to safeguard the strands. Protecting the hair up to 230C, the formula helps to reduce the breakage and damage caused by heat styling.

I have No more frizz, and my hair isn't weighed down. I feel like I'm wearing someone else's hair. The Smell is nice, not overpowering. (That's usually what bothers me the most.)
